content_description: A group of friends jumping on a trampoline while one person in the center tries to stand up amidst the bouncing.

High.reason: Intense jumping and chaotic movement as the person in the middle is bounced around vigorously.

Medium.reason: The person in the middle successfully stands up and the group celebrates with moderate movement.

Low.reason: A brief moment of relative stability as the person in the middle prepares to stand up between jumps.
